{
  "stem": "16571.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were taken to the local nick, put in behind bars, questions about, where is this gun?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we tried to explain, there was no gun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, in our own Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I-- I can't swear for certain, but I can 75% that one or two of the bigger ones got beatings from the British soldiers, asking, where is this gun?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I may also add, on the way to this-- to this nick, we were passing a hairdresser's, and I just had about a half an inch or an inch of hair.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was thinking, oh, they're not gonna cut my hair  off, they're not gonna cut my hair off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I-- I was jerking so bad, they're going to do something to us and cut my hair off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We passed-- we just walked past this hairdresser's, and we were kept three, four, or five days in this police station.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually, we were take in front of an officer with a German lady interpreter, which was killing me-- and I'm sure the others felt the same-- saying we cannot-- we could not find the gun.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you appear in front of us again, you'll be locked up for a long time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how it was later-- many years later, and that is just a little experience, what happened to us after the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And gradually, as I said, slowly, you found out that people were registering to go to Palestine one day, America another day, Britain another day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every-- every other day, I registered to go somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I registered with two of my best friends to come to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As I was the only one who was under 16, I was the only one chosen.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
